Package: gridkernel
Type: Package
Title: Package to apply kernels to raster data with NA and edge correction
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Ethan Plunkett
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.1)
Suggests: texmex, gridprocess
Maintainer: Ethan Plunkett <ethan@plunkettworks.com>
Description: This package applies  a  kernel to every cell in a grid returning
    a grid of the same  dimension  where each cell is replaced by the sum of the
    element wise product of the kernel  and  corresponding cells around the focal 
    cell.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
LinkingTo: Rcpp
